reviews.text:
This typical Hong Kong style small chain restaurant has been around for many years in the public estates in Hong Kong.   

Reasonable price,  reasonable quality. No nonsense,  no gimmick, no service charge no tips required,  they serve breakfast lunch afternoon tea and dinner for the hoods for many years.  We all need such down to earth joint in life in my opinion,  and this one was mine.

Octopus accepted.

reviews.text: 實果僅存！屋村茶餐廳。勁有風味！員工制服亦都好八十年代。香港味十足🥰

屋邨茶記，味道可以。餐牌雖然多年未變，但勝在品種多。
午餐、下午茶價錢同份量合理。
晚餐一般，比樓下大集團貴小許。
